➜【干货分享】云南澜沧江云南茶的母亲河普洱茶的原产地
http://www.sohu.com/a/436931481_100049042	7981
<p class="ql-align-center">澜沧江畔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">澜沧江峡谷，摄影师@李珩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/4d9d7a743d0f4bc3825e98aeeb80e143.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云南是普洱茶原产地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而澜沧江则是云南茶（普洱茶和滇红）的母亲河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前业内以普洱茶品质特征</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要分为四大产区（未列保山）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沿澜沧江从北至南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">普洱茶大产区分布其周围：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">临沧、普洱（思茅）、勐海、易武</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云南不似中原地区四季分明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云南只分雨季和旱季</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雨季高温多雨多日照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旱季低温干燥日照少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故茶质春茶普遍蜜香带甜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谷花茶苦涩较重</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雨水茶则水薄、苦较不化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（茶山树林，摄影@Ken.）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2970ee06ebff4d0d9a66f7a73dd643da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
